STATE EX REL. DOE
v.
OHIO STATE UNIV. 2019-0713 Supreme Court of Ohio. June 17, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULING

In Mandamus. On motion for admission pro hac vice of Kimberly Lau. Motion granted. Pursuant to Gov.Bar R. XII(4), counsel shall file a notice of permission with the Supreme Court's Office of Attorney Services within 30 days.
